{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grow your appetite for fossil hunting as the new <i><strong>junior</strong></i>\u00a0paleontologist in town! This demo is designed to be representative of the core game loop and ambience of &quot;<i>Goodlands</i>.&quot; It includes loads of NPCs, several quests, four dig sites (contributing to one full skeleton), a fossil cleaning mini game, 8 invertebrate fossils to collect, and 18 achievements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Things to look forward to in the full release:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Expanded map</u> with a lot more NPCs, quests, and collectables</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><i><strong>Prehistoric</strong></i> fishing</u> in crater lake inspired by creatures of the Western Interior Seaway</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Truck upgrades</u> (boost, winch, sonar, etc.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Expanded museum</u> with room for <strong>12-14 skeletons</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Improved fossil cleaning game</u>\u00a0(more tools, complexity, win/lose conditions, etc.)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Better character customization</u> (more options, more dinos &amp; co. to choose from)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Full gamepad and steam deck support</u>\u00a0(both work well with this demo)</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>Meaningful narrative thread</u></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;<i>Goodlands</i>&quot; is still in development and nothing is set in stone, so please give me your feedback. You can help shape this game into something truly special.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"New Paleontologist in Town","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1806020/e6a984bef77e0f3a54998e859fd6b130b35aad01.jpg"},{"name":"It's the Little Things...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps